properties.Name: AtmLocationType
properties.Description:
A categorization of ATM location based upon the host function performed at that location.

Ex:
- Airport
- Grocery stores 
- Gas stations 
- Discount superstores 
- Book stores 
- Ticket counters (concert tickets, airline tickets, etc.) 
- Pharmacies 
- Hotels 
- E-tailers 
- Restaurants

Columns.Name: AtmLocationTypeId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of the ATM Location Type.

Columns.Name: AtmLocationName
Columns.Description: The name of the ATM Location Type.

Columns.Name: AtmLocationDescription
Columns.Description: The description of the ATM Location Type.
